<!doctype html><html lang="en"><head><meta charset="utf-8"><meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width,initial-scale=1"><meta name="color-scheme" content="dark"><title>QuickNovel Operations — Sign in</title><style>
  :root{--bg:#080b12;--panel:#121925;--line:#28354a;--text:#eff4fb;--muted:#8f9db1;--accent:#83e1c5;--danger:#ff8a98}*{box-sizing:border-box}body{margin:0;min-height:100vh;display:grid;place-items:center;padding:24px;background:radial-gradient(circle at 50% 0,rgba(76,142,174,.25),transparent 42%),var(--bg);color:var(--text);font-family:Inter,system-ui,sans-serif}.login{width:min(410px,100%);padding:30px;border:1px solid var(--line);border-radius:18px;background:linear-gradient(145deg,rgba(20,28,42,.98),rgba(12,17,26,.98));box-shadow:0 30px 70px rgba(0,0,0,.4)}.mark{display:grid;place-items:center;width:45px;height:45px;border-radius:14px;background:linear-gradient(145deg,var(--accent),#4c8eff);color:#061015;font-size:19px;font-weight:900}.eyebrow{margin-top:24px;color:var(--accent);font-size:10px;letter-spacing:.15em;text-transform:uppercase;font-weight:800}h1{font-size:25px;letter-spacing:-.04em;margin:7px 0 6px}p{color:var(--muted);font-size:12px;line-height:1.6;margin:0 0 23px}.field{display:grid;gap:6px;margin:14px 0}.field label{font-size:11px;font-weight:700}.field input{border:1px solid var(--line);background:#0a1019;color:var(--text);border-radius:9px;padding:12px;font:14px inherit;outline:none}.field input:focus{border-color:#76bdec;box-shadow:0 0 0 3px rgba(118,189,236,.1)}button{width:100%;margin-top:12px;border:0;border-radius:9px;background:var(--accent);color:#06110e;padding:12px;font:750 13px inherit;cursor:pointer}.error{border:1px solid rgba(255,138,152,.28);background:rgba(255,138,152,.08);color:var(--danger);padding:10px 12px;border-radius:9px;font-size:11px;margin-bottom:16px}.foot{text-align:center;color:#66758a;font-size:10px;margin-top:21px}
</style></head><body><section class="login"><div class="mark">Q</div><div class="eyebrow">Restricted console</div><h1>Operational control</h1><p>Sign in to inspect service health, trace requests, investigate failures and manage runtime controls.</p>{{#if error}}<div class="error">The username or password was not accepted.</div>{{/if}}<form method="post" action="/admin/login"><div class="field"><label for="username">Username</label><input id="username" name="username" value="{{username}}" autocomplete="username" required></div><div class="field"><label for="password">Password</label><input id="password" type="password" name="password" autocomplete="current-password" autofocus required></div><button type="submit">Sign in securely</button></form><div class="foot">Credentials are managed through the deployment environment.</div></section></body></html>
